text: Massieville is an unincorporated community in Ross County, in the U.S. state of Ohio. ==History== Variant names were "Massie" and "Waller". The community has the name of Waller Massie, the proprietor of a local sawmill. ==Notable person== Will Huff, a composer, was born at Massieville in 1875. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Ross County, Ohio Category:Unincorporated communities in Ohio
title: Massieville, Ohio
